      "value": "<p>While in Wild Shape form, you gain the following benefits.</p><p><strong>Lunar Radiance.</strong> Each of your attacks in a Wild Shape form can deal its normal damage type or Radiant damage. You make this choice each time you hit with those attacks.</p><p><strong>Increased Toughness.</strong> You can add your Wisdom modifier to your Consitituion saving throws.</p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-UMRrbq9806vLH52i\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>This feature includes an Active Effect which automates the bonus to saving throws, but it must be manually turned on while you are in Wild Shape form.</p></section>",
